question: Tī 2016 nî 12 goe̍h 31 ji̍t ê chòe-āu, ūi-tiâu kò͘-choá ê hāng-bo̍k chiap-chhiú ê chu-liāu siōng-chē?
Tsia e kui-choā nî ê 'consolidated balance' in-ū hō͘ 'foreign currency translation' hō͘-iâⁿ ê chha-siong, choân-pō͘ lóng sī hū ê hāu-ióng, ūi-chòe hō͘-tōaⁿ sī siáⁿ-chē?
Tī 2014 nî bóe, siáⁿ chi̍t ê khu he siōng chē chîⁿ ê, i tī 2017 nî bóe chha siáⁿ chîⁿ?
2014年底到2017年底，consolidated balance嘅逐年趨勢係點樣？
answer: Consolidated balance 嘅趨勢唔係線性嘅。佢由2014年底嘅 $2217.6 百萬大幅增加到2015年底嘅 $2500.4 百萬，到2016年底略微下降到 $2455.0 百萬，之後喺2017年底溫和回升到 $2479.6 百萬。

question: Oaⁿ-tiâu ê sèng-khoan sī ūi-tio̍h koh-iáu ê sî-kan, tùi 2015 nî 12 goe̍h 31 ji̍t kàu 2016 nî 12 goe̍h 31 ji̍t, bô piàn-tōng ê?
Tī 2014 nî 12 goe̍h 31 ji̍t ê consolidated khó-kiám tang-tiong, ū hūn chē chē chi̍t-pīⁿ ê kiám hō͘ 'public' phòan-sò͘?
Nā-sī 2015 nî ê chham-ka iōng-hêng nā-sī chhōe 100 pah-bān-gô͘ gîn-á khah sió, thì 2015 nî 12 go̍eh 31 ji̍t ê chóng-hē koan-îng thiaⁿ-chhù tio̍h ē sī sím-mih?
Tī chit ê chu-liāu lāi-bīn, siáⁿ chi̍t kiāⁿ tāi-chìⁿ hō͘ kong-liân hē-thóng chū 2014 nî îⁿ-té kàu 2015 nî îⁿ-té ê chéng-gia̍h tōa thiàu-tiâu?
answer: Chit ê 'chòe-sin kau-ōe' (acquisition) tāi-chìⁿ sī chú-iàu ê ín-chháu. I hiah ê kong-liân hē-thóng ê chéng-gia̍h chē 305.2 pah-bān bí-kim, chit-ê chha-piah chhiau-kòe 2014 nî ê 2217.6 pah-bān bí-kim kàu 2015 nî ê 2500.4 pah-bān bí-kim, to̍h-sī hâm-kè chē-chē chòe-sin kau-ōe ê chha-piah, to̍h-sī hâm-kè chē-chē choán-ōe.

question: Na-ti gîn-hâng hun-chiap ga̍k-á ū ài ēng '2014' lâi chòe 'cdw advanced services allocation' ê sū-kiāⁿ ê placeholder tsiat-chāi ê giâ-sòan?
Na-e siat-tiâu tiâu-chéng sū-bū (gōa-jī-sè tāi-sòan, sîng-chiap, í-ki̍t hun-pò) siōng-tōa ê kò͘-chong-ōe phò-hāi hō͘ kòng-chòe chè hē-thóng chòe-tōa ê kò͘-chong-ōe hāi-sún?
Tī 2014 nî 12 goe̍h 31 ji̍t kàu 2017 nî 12 goe̍h 31 ji̍t, lóng-chóng liân-ha̍p ê chi̍t-mîm ê seng-ti̍t sī nn̄g-chē?
